text: This early morning have a lot of fruit n sunshine bread 🍞 on 3am onward....  Only banana 🍌 will come on 9am onward....  Fresh veg on 6am onward if u want get vegi.... Almost every grocery will display out 👍👍

Bigger, Better & Bountiful! Just completed renovations with more Variety & Options.  New additions such as Roast Meat Delights, Fresh Pork With Butcher & Plenty of Tofu. It remains 24/7, serving the Buangkok neighborhood. 💪🏼👏🏼

At the moment, it is undergoing some renovation therefore limited choices of groceries and necessity. The smell of "construction" emanate the air. If you don't mind walking a little, there is a newly opened NTUC Fairprice Finest a stone throw away in Sengkang Grand Mall.
Glad to have this 24 hour branch in the neighbourhood. It has the basic stuff you need. Items get restocked rather slowly at times but still fine.

Ordered from grabmart GM-007, grabrider left out my frozen item and i immediately called Ntuc Compassvale and manage to speak to wendy..and refered to her TL..relate my issues and i have agreed to come down and collect...at first they wanted to deliver to me (its not their fault in the 1st place it was GRAB that missed out my orders)which i told them its ok i am willing to come down and collect. To my surprise, i was welcome by wendy and angie at the cashier, both are very polite and friendly especially angie.. kept apologising for the lapse although its not their fault but their professionalism is awesome. Plus a small token as gestures was given to me. I was really amazed on their customer service..once again thank angie ng and wendy..i will definitely come back and shop at ntuc compassvale😍😍😍
